  "notes": [
    "This study investigates the role of TRPV1 receptors in bladder-colon cross-sensitization using an animal model of colitis induced by TNBS.",
    "The paper demonstrates that resiniferatoxin (RTX) can reduce some aspects of cross-sensitization but may increase somatic hypersensitivity.",
    "The study provides evidence for differential effects of TRPV1 desensitization on visceral versus somatic pain pathways."
  ]
